# Reqruit IQ

AI-powered job recruitment platform — match candidates to jobs, rank with AI, and manage hiring pipelines.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Terminal 1 — Backend API
cd backend
npm install
npm start

# Terminal 2 — AI Service (optional)
cd recruit-ai
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn api:app --reload --port 8000
```

Open: **http://localhost:3001/frontend/home/index.html**

See [SETUP.md](SETUP.md) for full instructions, Supabase setup, and demo accounts.
